    ns1:description """<p>Hello All!!!</p>

<p>I am going to embark on writing a book about The Final Chapter (Death Stories). I have always felt this was a mission of mine since I did so many presentations surrounding this topic. My hopes are to dispel the collective fear society has placed on this transitional part of life.</p>

<p>I invite you to include any stories you may want to share. This will include:</p>

<ol>
<li><p>Dreams of the departed</p></li>
<li><p>Psychic synchronicity surrounding the death of someone</p></li>
<li><p>Dreams that prepare us for someone passing</p></li>
<li><p>People know when they are going to pass</p></li>
<li><p>People without a belief system about death</p></li>
<li><p>When people don't have a plan/idea about death</p></li>
<li><p>Ghosts - people who don't move on</p></li>
<li><p>Your NDE's</p></li>
<li><p>Experiences with pets who have passed</p></li>
<li><p>Death as an agent of social change</p></li>
</ol>

<p>I will also include tips:</p>

<ul>
<li><p>Re-entry into fearful dreams</p></li>
<li><p>Active imagination journeys to plan our exit</p></li>
<li><p>Dream transfers</p></li>
</ul>

<p>Please send me your stories! All will be anonymous in the telling.</p>

<p>Thank you!! Please forward to anyone who might have a story to share.</p>

<p>Star Edwards</p>

<p>text me also at 303-815-6704</p>

<p>starharp@comcast.net</p>
"""^^xsd:string ;
